    <detaileddescription>
<para>nanoflann is a C++ header-only library for building KD-Trees, mostly optimized for 2D or 3D point clouds.</para>
<para>nanoflann does not require compiling or installing, just an #include &lt;nanoflann.hpp&gt; in your code.</para>
<para>See:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><ulink url="https://github.com/jlblancoc/nanoflann">Online README</ulink></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ulink url="https://jlblancoc.github.io/nanoflann/">C++ API documentation</ulink> </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
